author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Basement pipe insulation tips…pipe penetrations through ceilings and walls create drafty homes. I use Great Stuff Gaps and Cracks Pro to solve this problem. I adjust the gun to make the foam the necessary size. And I seal any areas that cause cold air leaks into the finished space. Many thanks to Great Stuff for sponsoring this tutorial, visit greatstuff.dupont.com to learn which spray foam to use on your next project 👍🏽🔥#insulation #basementrenovation #greatstuff #brandpartner
